body:
>They know they aren't running against Hillary this time right...???

https://mobile.twitter.com/mguerra78628/status/1313845352055873544

So he wants biden's corruption investigated before biden is running for president, so they impeach saying he's abusing power to attack a political rival.  Now he's wanting clinton's corruption investigated and they're mad he's not going after a current political rival?  Insanity.
